{"id": "1245725087542280234", "channel_id": "1245725087542280234", "type": 0, "author_id": "1230083504285421578", "author_name": "qingshanzhiyin", "author_bot": false, "content": "刚进去打7-2，推荐61级，好的那我57级也能打吧？结果都什么东西啊，小怪一个个血又厚伤害高还有屏障，还动不动塞垃圾给你，我这阵容还不够好？（该升级的都升了）\n道中还要看造物看发牌，玩得那么痛苦那\n我抽卡是为了什么啊？？\n你boss关难打就算了，7-2就这样子那谁还乐意接着玩，上线前拿个普通点的账号试试吧", "timestamp": "2024-05-30T13:06:45.323000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🥲", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1245725088041668720", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-27-00-34-14-819_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 158882, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1245725087542280234/1245725088041668720/Screenshot_2024-05-27-00-34-14-819_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=6a0082e5&is=69ff3165&hm=2687e99e73bf39d392d0b6099c097200af99b6dd1e602dd6ef411eabd5ec136d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1245725087542280234", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "说真的第七章这个难度是不是有点离谱了", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
